org.springframework.cloud.netflix.zuul.filters.route

Class RibbonRoutingFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.zuul.ZuulFilter
      • org.springframework.cloud.netflix.zuul.filters.route.RibbonRoutingFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.netflix.zuul.IZuulFilter, Comparable<com.netflix.zuul.ZuulFilter>

    public class RibbonRoutingFilter
extends com.netflix.zuul.ZuulFilter
    Route ZuulFilter that uses Ribbon, Hystrix and pluggable http clients to send requests. ServiceIds are found in the RequestContext attribute FilterConstants.SERVICE_ID_KEY.
    Author:
    Spencer Gibb, Dave Syer, Ryan Baxter
